 Hololive的“家庭3D分发”是如何实现的？ Cover公司探秘追踪技术的幕后故事https://www.moguravr.com/hololive-3d-live-behind-the-scenes/ノンジャンル人生 Wed, 31 Jan 2024 10:46:16 +0000 VTuberホロライブおうち3D配信 https://www.moguravr.com/?p=244989 <p>运营 VTuber 机构“Hololive Productions”的 Cover Co., Ltd. 在一份官方说明中发布了用于“家庭 3D 分发”的部分虚拟形象技术。 （摘自Cover Co., Ltd.的官方说明）“Home 3D distribution”是[…]</p><p>帖子<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/hololive-3d-live-behind-the-scenes/">Hololive的“家庭3D分发”是如何实现的？ Cover 对跟踪技术的幕后观察</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>上。</p> ; <p>运营 VTuber 机构“ <a href="https://hololivepro.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hololive Productions</a> ”的<a href="https://cover-corp.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cover Co., Ltd.</a>在一份官方说明中发布了一些用于<strong>“家庭 3D 分发”</strong>的虚拟形象技术。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.y5nk0sm4qazc-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.y5nk0sm4qazc-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.y5nk0sm4qazc-jpg.webp 800w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.y5nk0sm4qazc-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.y5nk0sm4qazc-768x432.webp 768w" width="800" height="450" /></a><br /> （摘自<a href="https://note.cover-corp.com/n/n7a413a4c167b" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cover Co., Ltd.官方说明</a>）</p><p> “家庭3D分发”是一种允许Hololive Production所属的VTuber在家中而不是在工作室进行3D分发的系统。不仅上半身直播，还实现了全身直播，以及Hololive VTuber之间的3D协作，成为粉丝们的热门话题。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.d202j8fm9x3c-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.d202j8fm9x3c-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.d202j8fm9x3c-jpg.webp 800w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.d202j8fm9x3c-300x168.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.d202j8fm9x3c-768x430.webp 768w" width="800" height="448" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.pvaq6qtt8809-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.pvaq6qtt8809-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.pvaq6qtt8809-jpg.webp 800w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.pvaq6qtt8809-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.pvaq6qtt8809-768x432.webp 768w" width="800" height="450" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.x7rr1on935el-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.x7rr1on935el-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.x7rr1on935el-jpg.webp 800w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.x7rr1on935el-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.x7rr1on935el-768x432.webp 768w" width="800" height="450" /></a></p><p>标题为“关于支持家庭 3D 分发的跟踪系统”的官方说明解释了跟踪机制。 VTuber的面部表情使用iPhone的ARKit。他透露，身体运动使用多种跟踪输入，包括移动动作捕捉“ <a href="https://www.sony.jp/mocopi/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">mocopi</a> ”、使用键盘的行走动作和选择性动画。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="【首页3D凸等待】Pekomari被mocopi击败【Hololive/Hosho Marine/Pekora Usada】" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ym83gIIc7vs?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe><br /> （实际使用多个跟踪输入的流式传输）</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.55860jpwpqjm-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.55860jpwpqjm-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.55860jpwpqjm-jpg.webp 800w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.55860jpwpqjm-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.55860jpwpqjm-768x432.webp 768w" width="800" height="450" /></a></p><p>此外，还详细解释了Unity在计算人形模型姿态时的特殊情况。虽然内容严格来说是面向工程师的，但可以看出Hololive VTuber的3D分发并不是仅靠一套系统或设备实现的，而是多种技术融合的结果。</p><p>点击此处查看官方说明的详细信息。<br /> <a href="https://note.cover-corp.com/n/n7a413a4c167b" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://note.cover-corp.com/n/n7a413a4c167b</a></p><p> Cover Co., Ltd.一段时间以来一直在积极引进上述技术。此举看似是为了招募感兴趣领域的工程师，但通过公开公开那些不常在公开舞台上透露的专业技术部分，将为整个VTuber行业做出贡献。可以说，它连接到。</p><p> （参考）<a href="https://note.cover-corp.com/n/n7a413a4c167b" target="_blank" rel="noopener">官方说明</a></p><p>帖子<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/hololive-3d-live-behind-the-scenes/">Hololive的“家庭3D分发”是如何实现的？ Cover 对跟踪技术的幕后观察</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>上。</p> ;
曾经有过这样的音乐现场形式吗？利用透明LED实现虚拟与现实的融合“DOUBLE：”体验报告https://www.moguravr.com/double-report/けいろー Wed, 31 Jan 2024 09:55:06 +0000 VTuberActiv8 https://www.moguravr.com/?p=244919 <p> 2024 年 1 月 26 日。被誉为“现实与虚拟交叉的混合音乐节”的活动“DOUBLE:”在池袋harevutai举行。由 Activ8 赞助。它以创建 Kizuna AI 的公司而闻名 [...]</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/double-report/">使用透明 LED 实现虚拟与现实的融合：“DOUBLE：”体验报告</a>首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>上。</p> ; <p> 2024 年 1 月 26 日。被誉为“现实与虚拟交叉的混合音乐节”的活动“ <strong>DOUBLE：</strong> ”在池袋harevutai举行。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.h1qubtedmi7m-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.h1qubtedmi7m-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.h1qubtedmi7m-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.h1qubtedmi7m-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.h1qubtedmi7m-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.h1qubtedmi7m-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.h1qubtedmi7m-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p>由<a href="https://activ8.co.jp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Activ8</a>赞助。不仅以制作Kizuna AI而闻名，近年来还制作了《ONE PIECE FILM RED》中出现的歌的3DCG模型，支援了《PROJECT IM@S vα-liv》的制作，主持VRChat活动，参与虚拟直播节目“CAPSULE Live in VRChat “Metropulse””的现场制作。</p><p>本次活动由Activ8主办。其最大的特点是<strong>虚拟与现实相结合的混合制作</strong>。预告中强调，将采用“包括尖端透明LED在内的数字技术”，暗示这是有别于典型VTuber音乐现场的新尝试。</p><p>事实上，表演艺术家的阵容也别具一格。一位同时从事2D和3D创作的歌手，也是一位在音乐以外的领域也受到关注的创作者。活跃在舞曲主题角色项目前线的 DJ 兼音乐制作人。这也让人感觉他们正在挑选具有不同背景的艺术家，并受到广义上的“表达”的激励。</p><p>四位不同头衔和流派的艺术家将在 Activ8 主办的活动中进行表演，Activ8 已经制作了大量虚拟现场表演。如果是这样的话，我相信我们会看到一些新的作品和有趣的表达方式。在这篇文章中，我们将向您介绍一下备受期待的《DOUBLE:》。</p><h2>最先进的透明 LED 显示屏，投影图像清晰生动</h2><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="DOUBLE: Vol.1 预告片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/zvgWiVo5vGA?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “DOUBLE：”四位艺术家在一个全站立的现场剧院中为挤满观众的观众演唱和表演了近两个半小时。</p><p>我对整个现场表演的印象可以用一个词来概括： <strong>“我感受到了‘虚拟’表达方式的可扩展性，以及VTuber音乐现场作为一种真实‘体验’的潜力。”</strong>当然，最主要的前提是这是一场非常令人愉快的音乐现场表演。</p><p>最让我印象深刻的是预告片中提到的“<strong>最先进的透明LED</strong> ”。事实上，毫不夸张地说，这些透明LED是这场现场表演的关键。</p><p>首先，请看一下下面的图片。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.b69ykdchfkkm-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.b69ykdchfkkm-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.b69ykdchfkkm-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.b69ykdchfkkm-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.b69ykdchfkkm-768x512.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.b69ykdchfkkm-1536x1023.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.b69ykdchfkkm-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p>你明白吗？画面看起来像是三个元素的组合：虚拟效果（漩涡）、真实表演者（刀子）和背景图像（浅蓝色风景）。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.8ckgfe4ewwi-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.8ckgfe4ewwi-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.8ckgfe4ewwi-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.8ckgfe4ewwi-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.8ckgfe4ewwi-768x512.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.8ckgfe4ewwi-1536x1023.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.8ckgfe4ewwi-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p>此外，在上图中，虚拟的长濑由香透明地出现在真实的长濑由香面前。这到底是什么意思？</p><p>首先，在现实世界的一般现场音乐场所举办的“VTuber音乐现场”中，VTuber的图像被投影到舞台上设置的大型显示器上。虽然也有像虹山寺、Hololive等大型演唱会中常见的AR效果、芥末音乐学校的真人大小虚拟形象直播系统等特殊的变化，但“显示投影”风格是小规模演出的主流。中等规模的活动。你可以这么说。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.8k4bfgslkbsw-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.8k4bfgslkbsw-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.8k4bfgslkbsw-jpg.webp 960w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.8k4bfgslkbsw-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.8k4bfgslkbsw-768x432.webp 768w" width="960" height="540" /></a><br /> （一般中型VTuber直播，如果有真人表演者，经常会出现在屏幕前）</p><p>这次的《DOUBLE:》也以类似的风格投射了VTuber，但与过去有一些不同。<strong>舞台背景安装了全尺寸LED高清显示屏，除此之外，舞台上靠近观众席的地方还有一个大型透明LED显示屏，上面显示着VTuber/人物。正在投影它</strong>。</p><p>换句话说，如果你把它画成图表，它会是这样的：</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.5qokh1phehqt-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.5qokh1phehqt-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.5qokh1phehqt-jpg.webp 960w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.5qokh1phehqt-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.5qokh1phehqt-768x432.webp 768w" width="960" height="540" /></a><br /> （“DOUBLE：”的情况下：VTuber出现在蓝色的透明LED中）</p><p>这种透明 LED 的透明度令人惊叹。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.gzdtemj3zr4h-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.gzdtemj3zr4h-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.gzdtemj3zr4h-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.gzdtemj3zr4h-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.gzdtemj3zr4h-768x511.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.gzdtemj3zr4h-1536x1022.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.gzdtemj3zr4h-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.4luk8qlnxrzc-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.4luk8qlnxrzc-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.4luk8qlnxrzc-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.4luk8qlnxrzc-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.4luk8qlnxrzc-768x511.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.4luk8qlnxrzc-1536x1022.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.4luk8qlnxrzc-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p><strong>一旦你知道它在那里，它看起来很正常，但在表演之前，当赞助商的镜头被播放时，我不知道显示器是透明的。</strong>现场表演开始了，港白金女子学院的两位顶级击球手（黑铁玉和白金女子学院）出现在舞台上，当VJ开始在他们身后播放时，他们终于说：“我们正在使用两台显示器。”我明白了。如果我在观众面前，我可能会立刻注意到它，但至少从远处看我根本看不到它。</p><p>当我认识到透明 LED 的存在时，我对投射的图像之美感到惊讶。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.sr2v0u2ys9n6-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.sr2v0u2ys9n6-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.sr2v0u2ys9n6-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.sr2v0u2ys9n6-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.sr2v0u2ys9n6-768x511.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.sr2v0u2ys9n6-1536x1022.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.sr2v0u2ys9n6-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a><br /> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.msxqrwu3rwfc-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.msxqrwu3rwfc-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.msxqrwu3rwfc-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.msxqrwu3rwfc-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.msxqrwu3rwfc-768x511.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.msxqrwu3rwfc-1536x1022.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.msxqrwu3rwfc-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.l0o2mxicfj9m-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.l0o2mxicfj9m-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.l0o2mxicfj9m-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.l0o2mxicfj9m-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.l0o2mxicfj9m-768x511.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.l0o2mxicfj9m-1536x1022.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.l0o2mxicfj9m-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p>在投射角色的现场表演中，根据显示器的性能，颜色可能看起来很奇怪，或者您可能会看到闪烁或残像。然而，当天登场的港白金女子学院学园的两名学生，不仅站立的身影清晰投影，即使大幅移动，也没有丝毫不适和模糊感。<strong>飘逸的头发和摇曳的衣摆都被精美地描绘出来，就连激烈的舞蹈表演的锐利也被清晰地捕捉到。</strong></p><p>顺便说一句，除了一些例外，这次现场表演是允许摄影和录音的，但如果你写下“即使是智能手机相机也可以清晰地捕捉到透明LED上投射的人物和动作。”我不知道我是否可以传达只是一点点它是多么令人惊奇。实际表现已发布在“ <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/DOUBLE_XR?src=hashtag_click" target="_blank" rel="noopener">#DOUBLE_XR</a> ”上，有兴趣的请查看。</p><h2>透明 LED 和深度真实 x 虚拟混合体验扩展了“现场”表达</h2><p>顺便说一下，正如我之前在图中所解释的，两个显示器之间是原来的“真正表演者的舞台”。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.3lem1vgkc51-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.3lem1vgkc51-682x1024.webp" sizes="(max-width: 682px) 100vw, 682px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.3lem1vgkc51-682x1024.webp 682w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.3lem1vgkc51-200x300.webp 200w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.3lem1vgkc51-768x1153.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.3lem1vgkc51-1023x1536.webp 1023w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.3lem1vgkc51-jpg.webp 1066w" width="682" height="1024" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.f0y379ciwn7j-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.f0y379ciwn7j-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.f0y379ciwn7j-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.f0y379ciwn7j-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.f0y379ciwn7j-768x512.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.f0y379ciwn7j-1536x1023.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.f0y379ciwn7j-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.v6ybh44x4wt9-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.v6ybh44x4wt9-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.v6ybh44x4wt9-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.v6ybh44x4wt9-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.v6ybh44x4wt9-768x512.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.v6ybh44x4wt9-1536x1023.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.v6ybh44x4wt9-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p>也就是说，<strong>虽然有两个显示，但却是三层</strong>。真正的艺术家站在两个显示器之间，不仅利用背后的大显示器，还利用安装在观众一侧的透明LED，他们能够在一个有深度感的环境中进行表演。换句话说，它将<strong>虚拟制作带到了“真实”的一面</strong>。透明LED的存在不仅对VTuber有利，对真正的艺术家也有利。</p><p> ——现场表演的前半段我也是这么想的，但过了一段时间，我发现还有一层。表演过程中，通过观众看到的透明LED唱歌的<a href="https://twitter.com/Daok0" target="_blank" rel="noopener">道子</a>出现在显示屏前。客观地说，只是“正在唱歌的艺术家移到了舞台前面”，但那一刻，我感觉自己好像在空间中移动了，心想：“我可以来到‘这边’吗？” &#39; 也！？&#39;&#39;</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.21j43jmh8cum-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.21j43jmh8cum-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.21j43jmh8cum-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.21j43jmh8cum-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.21j43jmh8cum-768x512.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.21j43jmh8cum-1536x1023.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.21j43jmh8cum-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p>说到“来到这边”，我认为<a href="https://twitter.com/yuka_n_RIOT" target="_blank" rel="noopener">长濑由香</a>的存在和舞台在这场现场表演中具有象征意义，它促进了“真实与虚拟的混合”。<strong>长濑由香以虚拟歌手的形象出现，但瞬间变身为真正的歌手的作品。</strong>该场景包含在长濑本人发布的摘要视频中，因此请务必查看下面的帖子。令人惊奇的是它在瞬间发生了怎样的变化。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p dir="ltr" lang="ja">这是一个游乐场舞台，在这里您可以成为自己，而不会受到任何人的阻碍。</p><p>混合音乐节“DOUBLE:”<br />直播门票发售至今晚20:00，观看截止时间为今晚23:59。 <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f4e3.png" alt="📣" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></p><p>请看看XR的新可能性。<br />点击此处购买▼ <a href="https://t.co/7sG8d1YJw8">https://t.co/7sG8d1YJw8</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/DOUBLE_XR?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#DOUBLE_XR</a> <a href="https://t.co/iwl6hB7BhK">pic.twitter.com/iwl6hB7BhK</a></p><p> — 长濑由香 (@yuka_n_RIOT) <a href="https://twitter.com/yuka_n_RIOT/status/1751853493579808987?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 1 月 29 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.qci6jnte440d-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.qci6jnte440d-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.qci6jnte440d-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.qci6jnte440d-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.qci6jnte440d-768x512.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd