e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.qwpy9kqzmezz-1-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p>他们不仅从虚拟“快速变身”为实体，还展示了多种多样的表演，比如两人并肩唱歌、添加虚拟版本的自己（？）、来来去去等。在舞台上。 。</p><p>引起我注意的是长濑由香（实体）向观众走来唱歌的剪影，当她回到透明LED的另一边时，她融入了长濑由香和她的朋友们（虚拟）的剪影他们在舞台上走来走去。有一个场景，我有一瞬间看不到他。这是我第一次体验“三维空间中存在的人物消失在图像中”，这是一种奇怪的感觉。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.1usu642mhsax-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.1usu642mhsax-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.1usu642mhsax-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.1usu642mhsax-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.1usu642mhsax-768x512.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.1usu642mhsax-1536x1023.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.1usu642mhsax-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.628i89jg6fjo-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.628i89jg6fjo-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.628i89jg6fjo-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.628i89jg6fjo-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.628i89jg6fjo-768x512.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.628i89jg6fjo-1536x1023.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.628i89jg6fjo-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p dir="ltr" lang="ja">哪个才是真正的流量？<br />答案就是一切。 <a href="https://t.co/xbucifWbQx">https://t.co/xbucifWbQx</a></p><p> — 长濑由香 (@yuka_n_RIOT) <a href="https://twitter.com/yuka_n_RIOT/status/1751054199239081992?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 1 月 27 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><h2>尖端数字技术的试验场，梦想的扩展之地</h2><p>前后显示联动的歌词动画和几何图案的多重表达。在合唱《水星》时，与《烟火》同步，在舞台上爆炸的烟花闪光上投射出一个镜面球。 <strong>“DOUBLE:”的亮点之一是它利用前后重叠的两个显示器，融合了许多像这样的三维效果。</strong></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.vfetivw65x54-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.vfetivw65x54-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.vfetivw65x54-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.vfetivw65x54-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.vfetivw65x54-768x511.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.vfetivw65x54-1536x1022.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.vfetivw65x54-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.g8rxduaf361k-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.g8rxduaf361k-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.g8rxduaf361k-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.g8rxduaf361k-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.g8rxduaf361k-768x511.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.g8rxduaf361k-1536x1022.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.g8rxduaf361k-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.287lb0hou1et-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.287lb0hou1et-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.287lb0hou1et-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.287lb0hou1et-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.287lb0hou1et-768x512.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.287lb0hou1et-1536x1023.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.287lb0hou1et-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.o7qonpri5q5x-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.o7qonpri5q5x-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.o7qonpri5q5x-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.o7qonpri5q5x-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.o7qonpri5q5x-768x512.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.o7qonpri5q5x-1536x1023.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.o7qonpri5q5x-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.c6l5sat7pk6z-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.c6l5sat7pk6z-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.c6l5sat7pk6z-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.c6l5sat7pk6z-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.c6l5sat7pk6z-768x512.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.c6l5sat7pk6z-1536x1023.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.c6l5sat7pk6z-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p>另一方面，透明 LED 并不总是在真正的艺术家表演中使用。因此，当在关键场景中投射出三维效果时，你能感受到图像特有的缓慢和缓慢，仿佛突然出现在你的眼前。</p><p>一系列使用透明LED的表演可以被认为是所谓的“AR”式表现。不过，就我个人而言，它的感觉可能类似于VR音乐视频和粒子现场表演中经常看到的“视觉插孔”（表演不像VR中那样跟随你的头部运动，所以这是一种自然现象）完全不同的事情）。</p><p>另外一点是音响效果非常好，与视觉效果同步，增强了表演的真实感。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.fwcqpxohtvgx-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.fwcqpxohtvgx-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.fwcqpxohtvgx-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.fwcqpxohtvgx-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.fwcqpxohtvgx-768x511.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.fwcqpxohtvgx-1536x1022.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.fwcqpxohtvgx-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a><br /> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.7s75fsnnj2xv-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.7s75fsnnj2xv-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.7s75fsnnj2xv-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.7s75fsnnj2xv-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.7s75fsnnj2xv-768x512.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.7s75fsnnj2xv-1536x1023.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.7s75fsnnj2xv-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.29ftbk77cnbc-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.29ftbk77cnbc-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.29ftbk77cnbc-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.29ftbk77cnbc-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.29ftbk77cnbc-768x512.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.29ftbk77cnbc-1536x1023.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.29ftbk77cnbc-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.yvq8a2m28n9y-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.yvq8a2m28n9y-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.yvq8a2m28n9y-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.yvq8a2m28n9y-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.yvq8a2m28n9y-768x512.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.yvq8a2m28n9y-1536x1023.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.yvq8a2m28n9y-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p>当两个色彩暴力的迷幻主播叠加在引起身体核心共鸣的深沉低音之上时，你几乎会放下思绪，去旅行。这是一种现场体验，视觉和听觉都留给舞台上的艺术家，就像整个身体都沉浸在音乐中一样。特别是tofubeats的表现令人惊叹，因为使用AI的VJ制作以一种很好的方式欺骗​​了我的大脑，所以我希望看到它在其他俱乐部活动中使用。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p dir="ltr" lang="ja">我是一个使用 AI 实时生成豆腐节拍的 VJ <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/DOUBLE_XR?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#DOUBLE_XR</a> <a href="https://t.co/SnTty0KjIo">pic.twitter.com/SnTty0KjIo</a></p><p> — Toshikuni (@Toshikuni_Mayor) <a href="https://twitter.com/Toshikuni_Mayor/status/1750857992877355252?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 1 月 26 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>当我回顾整个现场表演时，上面提到的表演和表情，<strong>我首先想到的是：“我没想到仅仅增加一个显示器就可以将表情范围扩大这么多。”</strong> .”</p><p>当然，这并不只是添加一台显示器那么简单。毫无疑问，采用的是高性能、高品质的LED显示屏，而要达到纵深效果的系统必须是经过精心调整后才得以实施的。另外，还要考虑VJ要让观众有更强的立体感，声音要让观众没有不舒服的感觉，大家可以想象一下。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p dir="ltr" lang="ja"> 2024/1/26 “双：”<br />在池袋harevutai</p><p> Huez 负责指导、灯光和 VJ！<br />非常感谢！ <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/DOUBLE?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#DOUBLE</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/DOUBLE_XR?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#DOUBLE_XR</a> <a href="https://t.co/btQBIUGsk5">pic.twitter.com/btQBIUGsk5</a></p><p> — Huez (Huez) (@huez_official) <a href="https://twitter.com/huez_official/status/1750872758697996468?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 1 月 26 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>然而，站在观众的角度来看，他们真的很兴奋，我不禁思考这个实验的“未来”。<strong>仅在这场现场表演中就使用了各种各样的表现技术，但我相信他们可以通过透明 LED 做得更多</strong>。除了将其投影到显示器上之外，它似乎还可以用于现场表演以外的领域，例如新形式的VTuber音乐现场表演、与真正艺术家的合作、戏剧表演和时装秀。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.st67tl6tij8g-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.st67tl6tij8g-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.st67tl6tij8g-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.st67tl6tij8g-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.st67tl6tij8g-768x511.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.st67tl6tij8g-1536x1022.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.st67tl6tij8g-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.hbk3zkxf9x6k-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.hbk3zkxf9x6k-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.hbk3zkxf9x6k-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.hbk3zkxf9x6k-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.hbk3zkxf9x6k-768x512.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.hbk3zkxf9x6k-1536x1023.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.hbk3zkxf9x6k-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.osg6tosl77yl-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.osg6tosl77yl-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.osg6tosl77yl-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.osg6tosl77yl-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.osg6tosl77yl-768x511.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.osg6tosl77yl-1536x1022.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/