这个视频太棒了！本周推荐 VTuber 视频（截至 1 月 26 日） https://www.moguravr.com/vtuber-weekly-23-1-29/たまごまご Mon, 29 Jan 2024 10:30:00 +0000 VTuberFlare Runeえのぐさくらみこ三珠さくまる天宵家宝鐘マリン柚子花樋口楓獅白ぼたん現実みろ白上フブキ https://www.moguravr.com/?p=244709 <p> Vtuber尝试巨型书法！ ！ Sanju Sakumaru 是一位将虚拟外表融入现实的艺人 VTuber。这次我们在现实空间里写巨幅书法。它是如此的熟悉，以至于当你从远处看它时，你会一时分不清[...]</p><p>帖子这个<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/vtuber-weekly-23-1-29/">视频太棒了！本周推荐的 VTuber 视频（截至 1 月 26 日）</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>上。</p> ; <p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/387e2f4ec44485bdaa520ed6ee92bac3-kix.naj10xmov0c0-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/387e2f4ec44485bdaa520ed6ee92bac3-kix.naj10xmov0c0-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1015px) 100vw, 1015px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/387e2f4ec44485bdaa520ed6ee92bac3-kix.naj10xmov0c0-jpg.webp 1015w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/387e2f4ec44485bdaa520ed6ee92bac3-kix.naj10xmov0c0-300x168.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/387e2f4ec44485bdaa520ed6ee92bac3-kix.naj10xmov0c0-768x430.webp 768w" width="1015" height="568" /></a></p><h2> Vtuber尝试巨型书法！ ！ </h2><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Vtuber尝试巨型书法！ ！" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/lINQ5f1pE2A?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Sanju <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@mitamasakumaru" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Sakumaru 是</strong></a>一位将虚拟外表融入现实的艺人 VTuber。这次我们在现实空间里写巨幅书法。我惊讶地发现，它是如此的熟悉，以至于当你远远地看它时，你会一瞬间认不出它来。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/387e2f4ec44485bdaa520ed6ee92bac3-kix.hg6i4ilttgeg-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/387e2f4ec44485bdaa520ed6ee92bac3-kix.hg6i4ilttgeg-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1017px) 100vw, 1017px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/387e2f4ec44485bdaa520ed6ee92bac3-kix.hg6i4ilttgeg-jpg.webp 1017w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/387e2f4ec44485bdaa520ed6ee92bac3-kix.hg6i4ilttgeg-300x167.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/387e2f4ec44485bdaa520ed6ee92bac3-kix.hg6i4ilttgeg-768x428.webp 768w" width="1017" height="567" /></a></p><p>这个内容让你意识到虚拟现实并不特殊，而是理所当然地出现在现实世界中，这是多么有趣。最重要的是，最大的亮点是，尽管它是虚拟的，但它实际上作用于真实的事物。选择巨型书法作为主题，这对于 YouTuber 的视频来说也是独一无二的，这并不常见。值得注意的是相机角度的多样性。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="[挑战] Vtuber尝试了Kaburyuuma！ ！ ！ 【世界第一】" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/sPgfRM8tTdE?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>我还尝试各种其他挑战，例如用我的 VTuber 身体进行流镝马。克服作为 VTuber 的不适的技巧与紧凑而有趣的视频项目的结合是只有 Sanju Sakumaru 达到的状态，并且未来很可能会继续娱乐。</p><h2> 【敢于反其道而行之】咖啡科学/实验分布从失败中学习【正则分布#70】 </h2><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="【敢于反其道而行之】咖啡科学/实验分布从失败中学习【正则分布#70】" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/h5aUCFAuL2s?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>咖啡信息公司<a href="https://www.youtube.com/@amayoike" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Tenyoya</strong></a>决定尝试一下冲泡咖啡时应该注意什么和不应该做什么。据说不应该用 100 摄氏度的沸水冲泡咖啡，但为什么呢？让我们尝试一下并找出原因。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/387e2f4ec44485bdaa520ed6ee92bac3-kix.9h55455zxy5-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/387e2f4ec44485bdaa520ed6ee92bac3-kix.9h55455zxy5-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1015px) 100vw, 1015px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/387e2f4ec44485bdaa520ed6ee92bac3-kix.9h55455zxy5-jpg.webp 1015w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/387e2f4ec44485bdaa520ed6ee92bac3-kix.9h55455zxy5-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/387e2f4ec44485bdaa520ed6ee92bac3-kix.9h55455zxy5-768x434.webp 768w" width="1015" height="573" /></a></p><p>我们在实际比较饮料的同时解释了不同的热水倒入方式如何产生差异。咖啡的味道等差异很难解释，但由于这两个人都是销售方面的专家，所以听他们的话就很容易理解。<br />如果您是咖啡爱好者，有很多事情您可能从未尝试过。然而，这是一个有趣的广播，它是一个重新考虑我们处理美味咖啡的方式的机会。</p><h2> 【#hololive老网竞猜赛】hololive老网表情包竞猜赛</h2><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="【#hololive老网竞猜赛】hololive老网表情包竞猜赛" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/y6GgSmiMYCQ?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><a href="https://www.youtube.com/@ShirakamiFubuki" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>白神吹雪</strong></a>频道举办的问答活动充满了所有观众都想共同思考的话题。这是一个网络模因测验，主要基于 2000 年代初的 2channel 和 Niconico Douga 的互联网。参加者四人分别是： <a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCCzUftO8KOVkV4wQG1vkUvg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>宝生玛琳</strong></a>、 <a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC-hM6YJuNYVAmUWxeIr9FeA" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>樱美子</strong></a>、 <a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCUKD-uaobj9jiqB-VXt71mA" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>四四郎牡丹</strong></a>、 <a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCtyWhCj3AqKh2dXctLkDtng" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>一条梨香</strong></a>。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/387e2f4ec44485bdaa520ed6ee92bac3-kix.ufo0ghw7j2ea-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/387e2f4ec44485bdaa520ed6ee92bac3-kix.ufo0ghw7j2ea-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1015px) 100vw, 1015px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/387e2f4ec44485bdaa520ed6ee92bac3-kix.ufo0ghw7j2ea-jpg.webp 1015w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/387e2f4ec44485bd